# Output directories generated by run_sample.sh in each sample.
# These are transient execution artefacts, not part of the sample itself.
*/input/
*/build/
*/md/

# Exception: ketoprofen_pubchem ships a pre-downloaded SDF under input/.
# Re-include the directory, then re-ignore auto-generated files inside.
!ketoprofen_pubchem/input/
ketoprofen_pubchem/input/component_*.pdb
ketoprofen_pubchem/input/config.json

# Sub-level generation artefacts (stale output from the pre-normalisation layout)
*/pentane_benzene/
